      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.55,
      "size": 40752,
      "text": "欢迎来到勾股定理实验！今天我们要学习几何学中最著名的定理之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "勾股定理揭示了直角三角形三边之间的神奇关系，已有数千年的历史。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "在中国古代叫做勾三股四弦五，在西方叫做毕达哥拉斯定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "theorem-1",
      "filename": "theorem-theorem-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/theorem-theorem-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "勾股定理说：在直角三角形中，两条直角边的平方和等于斜边的平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "theorem-2",
      "filename": "theorem-theorem-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/theorem-theorem-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.18,
      "size": 50832,
      "text": "用公式表示就是a平方加b平方等于c平方，其中a和b是直角边，c是斜边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "theorem-3",
      "filename": "theorem-theorem-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/theorem-theorem-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "斜边是直角三角形中最长的边，它对着直角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "theorem-4",
      "filename": "theorem-theorem-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/theorem-theorem-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "这个定理可以用来求直角三角形中任意一边的长度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "visualization-1",
      "filename": "visualization-visualization-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/visualization-visualization-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "图中蓝色的三角形就是直角三角形，直角用小方块标记。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "visualization-2",
      "filename": "visualization-visualization-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/visualization-visualization-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "红色正方形的面积是a平方，绿色正方形的面积是b平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "visualization-3",
      "filename": "visualization-visualization-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/visualization-visualization-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.76,
      "size": 44208,
      "text": "勾股定理告诉我们，这两个正方形的面积之和等于斜边上正方形的面积c平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "visualization-4",
      "filename": "visualization-visualization-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/visualization-visualization-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "你可以勾选显示正方形来观察这个面积关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "proof",
      "line_id": "proof-1",
      "filename": "proof-proof-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/proof-proof-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "切换到几何证明模式，我们用面积法来证明勾股定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "proof",
      "line_id": "proof-2",
      "filename": "proof-proof-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/proof-proof-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "在直角边上分别构建正方形，边长为a的正方形面积是a平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "proof",
      "line_id": "proof-3",
      "filename": "proof-proof-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/proof-proof-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "边长为b的正方形面积是b平方，两者之和是a平方加b平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "proof",
      "line_id": "proof-4",
      "filename": "proof-proof-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/proof-proof-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.29,
      "size": 52560,
      "text": "在斜边上构建正方形，面积是c平方，通过几何变换可以证明它等于a平方加b平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "proof",
      "line_id": "proof-5",
      "filename": "proof-proof-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/proof-proof-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "点击播放动画可以看到正方形逐渐出现的过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "line_id": "pythagorean-triples-1",
      "filename": "pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "满足a平方加b平方等于c平方的正整数组合叫做勾股数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "line_id": "pythagorean-triples-2",
      "filename": "pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.29,
      "size": 52560,
      "text": "最小的勾股数是3, 4, 5，因为3平方加4平方等于9加16等于25等于5平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "line_id": "pythagorean-triples-3",
      "filename": "pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "其他常见的勾股数有5, 12, 13和8, 15, 17。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "line_id": "pythagorean-triples-4",
      "filename": "pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "勾股数的倍数也是勾股数，比如6, 8, 10是3, 4, 5的两倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "line_id": "pythagorean-triples-5",
      "filename": "pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean/pythagorean-triples-pythagorean-triples-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "右侧有快速设置按钮，你可以点击查看这些勾股数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean",
      "section_id": "application",
